00:22:39,218 --> 00:22:44,062
There is terrible administrative details that come to light.

364
00:22:44,102 --> 00:22:49,166
She had gone into hospital a few months before she died

365
00:22:49,286 --> 00:22:53,750
and had listed on her hospital admission sheet as her next of kin, her bank manager,

366
00:22:55,132 --> 00:22:58,434
which is still one of those things that kind of wakes me up at night occasionally.

367
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:04,522
you know, and then there's all kinds of social and friends relationship, again, it's clear.

