00:23:16,448 --> 00:23:17,569
surprisingly life-affirming.

371
00:23:18,249 --> 00:23:22,291
Um, but you, you can definitely map a bunch of, you know, friends there of a, you know,

372
00:23:22,331 --> 00:23:26,113
this friend who was jealous, and this friend who had a secret crush, and this friend who

373
00:23:26,173 --> 00:23:26,754
rejected her.

374
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:33,535
There's a whole bunch of professional stuff about where her career took her and financial concerns.

375
00:23:33,595 --> 00:23:43,302
There's some kind of systems that underpin her upbringing and the questions of the history of race and racial prejudice in London.

376
00:23:44,543 --> 00:23:45,924
And all of these things are so...

377
00:23:48,683 --> 00:23:55,645
knottedly interconnected and produced these imperceptible, unpredictable, longitudinal,

378
00:23:55,745 --> 00:23:59,986
contradictory changes and effects on each other that even if we could make any kind

