00:24:05,167 --> 00:24:08,708
The thing is not navigable as a system and you're left with this choice of...

382
00:24:09,998 --> 00:24:12,600
of you can boil it down, but then you boil it down

383
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:13,901
to something that's reductive and misleading,

